  }, "v5"), mdx("p", null, "Khi c\xE1c s\u0129 quan c\u1EE7a vua \xCA-x\xEA-chia \u0111\u1EBFn c\xF9ng \xCA-sai, "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v6"
  }, "v6"), mdx("p", null, "th\xEC \xF4ng b\u1EA3o h\u1ECD r\u1EB1ng, \"H\xE3y n\xF3i v\u1EDBi ch\u1EE7 c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i nh\u01B0 sau: CH\xDAA ph\xE1n, '\u0110\u1EEBng s\u1EE3 \u0111i\u1EC1u c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i nghe. \u0110\u1EEBng kinh ho\u1EA3ng v\xEC l\u1EDDi c\u1EE7a c\xE1c \u0111\u1EA7y t\u1EDB vua A-xy-ri s\u1EC9 nh\u1EE5c ta. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v7"
  }, "v7"), mdx("p", null, "Nghe \u0111\xE2y! Ta s\u1EBD \u0111\u1EB7t m\u1ED9t th\u1EA7n linh trong vua A-xy-ri. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi s\u1EBD nghe ti\u1EBFng \u0111\u1ED3n khi\u1EBFn ng\u01B0\u1EDDi s\u1EBD tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 x\u1EE9 m\xECnh r\u1ED3i ta s\u1EBD khi\u1EBFn cho ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u1EBFt v\xEC g\u01B0\u01A1m t\u1EA1i \u0111\xF3.'\"Qu\xE2n A-xy-ri r\u1EDDi th\xE0nh Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem "), mdx("h6", {
