    "id": "v9"
  }, "v9"), mdx("p", null, "Vua nghe b\xE1o c\xE1o r\u1EB1ng Ti\u1EC7t-ha-ca , vua Cu-si c\u1EE7a Ai-c\u1EADp, \u0111ang k\xE9o \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\xE1nh m\xECnh. Khi vua A-xy-ri nghe v\u1EADy li\u1EC1n sai s\u1EE9 \u0111\u1EBFn n\xF3i v\u1EDBi vua \xCA-x\xEA-chia r\u1EB1ng, "), mdx("h6", {
