  }, "v10"), mdx("p", null, "\"H\xE3y b\u1EA3o \xCA-x\xEA-chia, vua Giu-\u0111a nh\u01B0 sau: \u0110\u1EEBng \u0111\u1EC3 th\u1EA7n m\xE0 ng\u01B0\u01A1i tin c\u1EADy ph\u1EC9nh g\u1EA1t. \u0110\u1EEBng tin l\u1EDDi th\u1EA7n \u0111\xF3 qu\u1EA3 quy\u1EBFt r\u1EB1ng Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng b\u1ECB trao v\xE0o tay vua A-xy-ri. "), mdx("h6", {
