    "id": "v16"
  }, "v16"), mdx("p", null, "L\u1EA1y CH\xDAA, xin l\u1EAFng tai nghe. Xin m\u1EDF m\u1EAFt ra nh\xECn. Xin h\xE3y nghe m\u1ECDi \u0111i\u1EC1u vua San-ch\xEA-r\xEDp \u0111\xE3 n\xF3i \u0111\u1EC3 s\u1EC9 nh\u1EE5c Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF h\u1EB1ng s\u1ED1ng. "), mdx("h6", {
