  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "H\u1ECD \u0111\xE3 n\xE9m nh\u1EEFng th\u1EA7n c\u1EE7a c\xE1c d\xE2n t\u1ED9c \u0111\xF3 v\xE0o l\u1EEDa nh\u01B0ng nh\u1EEFng th\u1EA7n \u0111\xF3 ch\u1EB3ng qua ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 g\u1ED7 v\xE0 \u0111\xE1 do tay ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\xE0m ra v\xEC th\u1EBF c\xE1c vua A-xy-ri \u0111\xE3 ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t ch\xFAng. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v19"
  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "L\u1EA1y CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF ch\xFAng t\xF4i xin h\xE3y gi\u1EA3i c\u1EE9u ch\xFAng t\xF4i kh\u1ECFi quy\u1EC1n l\u1EF1c vua A-xy-ri \u0111\u1EC3 c\xE1c n\u01B0\u1EDBc tr\xEAn \u0111\u1EA5t bi\u1EBFt r\u1EB1ng Ng\xE0i l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF duy nh\u1EA5t.\"Ch\xFAa tr\u1EA3 l\u1EDDi \xCA-x\xEA-chia "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v20"
  }, "v20"), mdx("p", null, "Sau \u0111\xF3 \xCA-sai, con trai A-m\u1ED1t nh\u1EAFn v\u1EDBi \xCA-x\xEA-chia nh\u01B0 sau, \"CH\xDAA, Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF c\u1EE7a \xCDt-ra-en, ph\xE1n: Ta \u0111\xE3 nghe l\u1EDDi ng\u01B0\u01A1i c\u1EA7u nguy\u1EC7n c\xF9ng ta v\u1EC1 San-ch\xEA-r\xEDp, vua A-xy-ri. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v21"
  }, "v21"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110\xE2y l\xE0 \u0111i\u1EC1u CH\xDAA ph\xE1n ngh\u1ECBch c\xF9ng San-ch\xEA-r\xEDp: Trinh n\u1EEF Xi-\xF4n gh\xE9t ng\u01B0\u01A1i v\xE0 s\u1EC9 nh\u1EE5c ng\u01B0\u01A1i; N\xF3 c\u01B0\u1EDDi nh\u1EA1o ng\u01B0\u01A1i khi ng\u01B0\u01A1i b\u1ECF ch\u1EA1y. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v22"
  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\u01B0\u01A1i ch\u1EBF gi\u1EC5u v\xE0 nh\u1EE5c m\u1EA1 ai? Ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\xE3 l\xEAn ti\u1EBFng ngh\u1ECBch c\xF9ng ai? Ng\u01B0\u01A1i ng\u1EA1o m\u1EA1n x\u1EA5c l\xE1o \u0111\u1ED1i v\u1EDBi ai? Ng\u01B0\u01A1i ngh\u1ECBch ta, \u0110\u1EA5ng Th\xE1nh c\u1EE7a \xCDt-ra-en! "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v23"
  }, "v23"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\xE3 sai s\u1EE9 \u0111\u1EBFn s\u1EC9 nh\u1EE5c CH\xDAA. Ng\u01B0\u01A1i n\xF3i, 'Nh\u1EDD v\xE0o v\xF4 s\u1ED1 qu\xE2n xa ta k\xE9o l\xEAn c\xE1c \u0111\u1EC9nh n\xFAi, l\xEAn c\xE1c n\xFAi cao nh\u1EA5t c\u1EE7a Li-b\u0103ng. Ta \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1ED1n ng\xE3 c\xE1c c\xE2y h\u01B0\u01A1ng nam v\xE0 c\xE1c c\xE2y th\xF4ng t\u1ED1t nh\u1EA5t c\u1EE7a n\xF3. Ta \u0111\xE3 l\xEAn \u0111\u1EBFn c\xE1c n\u01A1i xa nh\u1EA5t v\xE0 v\xE0o c\xE1c r\u1EEBng t\u1ED1t nh\u1EA5t c\u1EE7a n\xF3. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v24"
  }, "v24"), mdx("p", null, "Ta \u0111\xE3 \u0111\xE0o c\xE1c gi\u1EBFng trong c\xE1c n\u01B0\u1EDBc ngo\u1EA1i qu\u1ED1c v\xE0 u\u1ED1ng n\u01B0\u1EDBc t\u1EEB c\xE1c gi\u1EBFng \u0111\xF3. B\xE0n ch\xE2n ta \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m c\u1EA1n kh\xF4 h\u1EBFt c\xE1c s\xF4ng Ai-c\u1EADp.' "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v25"
  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "H\u1EE1i vua A-xy-ri, h\u1EB3n ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\xE3 nghe. T\u1EEB x\u01B0a ta, CH\xDAA, \u0111\xE3 d\u1EF1 li\u1EC7u vi\u1EC7c n\u1EA7y. T\u1EEB l\xE2u ta \u0111\xE3 tr\xF9 li\u1EC7u vi\u1EC7c \u0111\xF3, b\xE2y gi\u1EDD ta th\u1EF1c hi\u1EC7n ch\xFAng. Ta \u0111\xE3 cho ph\xE9p ng\u01B0\u01A1i bi\u1EBFn c\xE1c th\xE0nh ki\xEAn c\u1ED1 c\xF3 v\xE1ch th\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED1ng g\u1EA1ch v\u1EE5n. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v26"
  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "D\xE2n c\u01B0 c\xE1c th\xE0nh \u0111\xF3 r\u1EA5t y\u1EBFu \u1EDBt; ch\xFAng n\xF3 ho\u1EA3ng s\u1EE3 v\xE0 b\u1ECB s\u1EC9 nh\u1EE5c. Ch\xFAng nh\u01B0 c\u1ECF ngo\xE0i \u0111\u1ED3ng, nh\u01B0 c\u1ECF non, y\u1EBFu \u1EDBt, nh\u01B0 c\u1ECF tr\xEAn n\xF3c nh\xE0 b\u1ECB gi\xF3 thi\xEAu \u0111\u1ED1t tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi m\u1ECDc l\xEAn. "), mdx("h6", {
